    <name>Optimizing Navigation</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{928e71c5-4a88-402b-a9b5-06a023b5407f}{193}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.15,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:0}"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With a start page in place,
attention can then turn to other instructional design practices that can help
your adult learners navigate the learning environment efficiently and better
process the information, including:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Presenting
information in smaller segments (a practice known as “chunking”) to provide
information in a way that can be consumed within the short time allotments
available to adult learners.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Providing
frequent opportunities for learners to check their understanding and apply what
they’ve learned for a more active learning experience. Even a prompt that asks
learners to consider how the information may apply to their own experiences can
improve retention.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Including
summaries at the end of modules that highlight the big ideas and key
takeaways.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;



​&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{928e71c5-4a88-402b-a9b5-06a023b5407f}{208}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:0}"&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/divider%20wave.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
